	<h1 class="title">啊这些大象犀牛章鱼椅子，也太浮夸了</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/161922/small/161922.jpg?1442322894" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">廖婷 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-29 18:09:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/16781/medium/16781.jpg?1446096037" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


