	<div class="article-detail-bd">
			<div class="excerpt">
				感觉来到了改装过的史前生物陈列室。好啦，我知道什么是史前生物，就是这么一说。
			</div>
		<div class="detail">
				<!-- 普通文章 -->
				<p>
	西班牙艺术家 Maximo Riera 带来了他的动物椅子系列，章鱼、海象、犀牛、大象、河马、鲸鱼全都背上了一个欧洲古典风格的座位。因为是在画廊展出，仿真的大块动物搭配现代建筑，颇有生物入侵的感觉。
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/e3c814b19bb7.jpg" width="818" height="548" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/077ed2a754ff.jpg" width="950" height="949" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/9456bacfd8f1.jpg" width="818" height="545" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/805f48d70ef2.jpg" width="818" height="523" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/d2543d671d83.jpg" width="950" height="633" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/4fd5180b773c.jpg" width="818" height="824" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/48936e57f152.jpg" width="818" height="546" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/999ea35b6dbc.jpg" width="950" height="633" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/0a78912fec1f.jpg" width="818" height="614" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/8b21c0d9fe28.jpg" width="818" height="538" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/0e9b5e8e7fd8.jpg" width="818" height="556" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/8f5903d6497e.jpg" width="504" height="650" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	<span>每一个动物座椅都是高密度聚氨酯的材料做的，内部用铁来支撑，有弹性且能持久使用。为了确保精确，设计师从 3D 建模开始，然后进行人工切割，每一个都要花上大概 480 小时，换算成实际工作量达到了 9 周到 11 周。这个系列已经在不同的地方展出并持续更新，甚至可以售卖。</span><a href="http://maximoriera.com/animal-chair-collection/" target="_blank">这里是他的主页。</a> 
</p>
<p>
	不过，这些椅子都是重量级的，大象椅子甚至重达 125 千克，<span>算得上半个雕塑了。</span>恐怕更适合出现在酒店之类的场所（买一个镇镇场子就够了）。
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/0528a50e3945.jpg" width="950" height="534" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/838fa13e44b2.jpg" width="950" height="534" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/695f451f92fd.jpg" width="950" height="534" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/52ef391f7583.jpg" width="950" height="534" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/19881d8b3992.jpg" width="950" height="534" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="http://cms.qdaily.com/uploads/image/201510/926ba6c805a4.jpg" width="950" height="637" title=" " alt=" " style="text-align:center;" /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	图片来自&nbsp;<a href="http://www.designboom.com/art/maximo-riera-animal-chair-collection-new-edition-10-29-2015/" target="_blank">designboom</a>、<a href="http://maximoriera.com/gallery/" target="_blank">maximoriera</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
